## Definition of done ("fully running, tested, vetted") — ✅ MET 2026-07-07

1. [x] Fresh machine: `reactable agent pull` → chat offline, no HF account (pull path + offline status verified)
2. [x] `just smoke-agent` (4/0), `just test-agent-stub` (13/0), `just validate-agent-e2e` (15/0, 1 manual-UI) all exit 0
3. [x] G1 history fix + G2 sandbox decisions merged; escape probes hard-green (stub T7–T10 + e2e leak probe)
4. [x] Latency in budget: cold 6.9 s, warm 6.5 s, invoke-rate 3/3 — recorded above
5. [x] G5 (multimodal) + token-streaming explicitly deferred

**Residual (not blocking DoD):** token streaming (nexus SSE), self-hosted stub CI runner, G5 vision via mlx-vlm.

